[30;1m53 | [0m[35mclass ConfigurationLoader(Protocol):[0m
[30;1m54 | [0m[35m    """[0m
[30;1m55 | [0m[35m    The ApiConfigurationLoader is responsible for populating the API and Proxy configuration from a [0m
[30;1m56 | [0m[35m    environment variables with preference given to the secrets file.[0m
[30;1m57 | [0m[35m    """[0m
